1807, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.6964534547602764, \"rank\": 0.4252959079984362, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 1811, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.6964534547602764, \"rank\": 0.4252959079984362, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To that end, he has been removed from our commentary roster with immediate effect.\\\"\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Monday, July 29, Ballard posted a statement onXapologizing if his remarks had offended viewers.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The comments I made during the Australian freestyle relay victory ceremony on Saturday have caused some offense.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999983238333648, \"rank\": 1.5523419460134319e-06, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was never my intention to upset or belittle anyone, and if I did, I apologize.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a massive advocate of women's sport,\\\" said Ballard, who has been covering global sports since the 1980s and is best known for his coverage of swimming and diving.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimmers-Mollie O'Callaghan,Emma McKeon,Meg Harris, andShayna Jack-were waving to crowds and celebrating the fourth Olympics in a row where Australia has claimed the gold medal in the event when Ballard made his comments.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}, {\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}, {\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meg Harris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\"}, {\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meg Harris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\"}, {\"begin\": 2794, \"end\": 2803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9875770600757056, \"rank\": 0.00940582731096731, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2849, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His co-commentator and British swimming champion,Lizzie Simmonds, immediately branded his remark \\\"outrageous,\\\" prompting laughter from Ballard.\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2900, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Swimming\"}, {\"begin\": 3012, \"end\": 3019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his statement on X, Ballard urged fans not to \\\"pile in on\\\" Simmonds, as some had been quick to attack the ex-Olympic swimmer online.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3045, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.7274144669887602, \"rank\": 0.37044567216932733, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Us:  About Us  Legal  News  Connect\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3198, \"entities\": []}]}"